{
  "text": "Two studies have examined infant media use and subsequent attention problems in school-aged children. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] One of these studies found that the effects of television watching on infants' attention span varied with the content of the programming.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "143063373",
